reviewText: I work in the medical field and this is very eye opening and refreshing to see doctors doing house calls, less chances of going to hospitals,nursing homes.  I would recommend this to anyone that wants to have health care like this again.

Excellent look at a new way of medical care with a better doctor patient relationship.  Somewhat dim view, unexplained, of the Indian Health Service in Alaska.  For all that, a quite informative and hopeful view of the future of medicine.
